ZH: 他们通过决议决定了下一步的行动计划。
EN: They decided on the next course of action through a resolution.

ZH: 联合国的决议呼吁各国采取协调行动。
EN: The United Nations' resolution called for coordinated action by all countries.

ZH: 我们将按照决议的要求进行行动。
EN: We will act according to the resolution's requirements.

ZH: 通过这个决议，我们可以解决当前的争端。
EN: Through this resolution, we can resolve the current dispute.

ZH: 请投票表决这个决议案。
EN: Please vote to decide on this resolution.

ZH: 这个决议是为了促进全球经济合作而制定的。
EN: This resolution was formulated to promote global economic cooperation.

ZH: 他们达成了一项决议，以结束长期的纠纷。
EN: They reached a resolution to put an end to the long-standing dispute.

ZH: 决议的执行将在接下来的几个月内开始。
EN: The implementation of the resolution will begin in the coming months.

ZH: 请大家遵守决议的规定。
EN: Please adhere to the provisions of the resolution.

ZH: 决议的通过标志着一个新的篇章的开始。
EN: The adoption of the resolution marks the beginning of a new chapter.

ZH: 他们通过表决通过了这个决议案。
EN: They passed this resolution through a vote.

ZH: 这个决议将有助于解决当前的人权问题。
EN: This resolution will help address the current human rights issues.

ZH: 大家一致通过了这个决议。
EN: Everyone unanimously passed this resolution.

ZH: 决议的通过得到了全体成员的支持。
EN: The resolution's adoption received the support of all members.

ZH: 与决议相符，我们将采取相关的行动。
EN: In accordance with the resolution, we will take appropriate action.

ZH: 这个决议明确规定了措施的具体细节。
EN: This resolution clearly outlines the specific details of the measures.

ZH: 他们争论了很久才最终通过了这个决议。
EN: They debated for a long time before finally passing this resolution.

ZH: 这个决议将在所有会员国间生效。
EN: This resolution will come into effect among all member states.

ZH: 请提出你对这个决议的建议。
EN: Please propose your suggestions on this resolution.

ZH: 他们在会议中提出了一个有关动议来修改决议草案。
EN: They presented a motion during the meeting to amend the resolution draft.
